  Feedback:
We may ask you to provide feedback on our Services
  through various means of communications such as through our App, Direct
  Marketing (as defined above), or otherwise through third party survey
  platforms. If you choose to address our request for such feedback or
  participate in our survey, we will collect your feedback (as provided, i.e.,
