  training and machine learning purposes, subject to obtaining your consent.
  You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time, as set forth under
  Section 8
Your Rights
, below, or
  through the App’s Privacy Settings.
AI Training Data will be permanently deleted
  within 2 years after we process them for training purposes, unless we are
  legally required to maintain the data for a longer period. We will also
  delete AI Training Data if you withdraw consent for Lightricks to use your
  personal data to improve our services though AI machine learning, you ask us
  to delete all your information and your account, or in accordance with our
  data retention policies.
Please note that we do our best to moderate the
setting of the AI Tools Output to not include any inappropriate or harmful
content, however, it is your sole responsibility to upload images, photos,
videos, audio recordings and other content that is not unlawful, libelous,
defamatory, obscene, pornographic, indecent, lewd, suggestive, harassing,
threatening, invasive of privacy or publicity rights, abusive, inflammatory,
fraudulent, or can be otherwise interpreted as harmful content. Please contact
us at
dpo@lightricks.com
if you find
any content to be offensive.
